OL,3,CChurch in Wales announces first female
OL,4,CArchbishop
OL,6,FThe Bishop of Monmouth, Cherry Vann,
OL,7,Fwill become the Church in Wales' first
OL,8,Ffemale and openly gay Archbishop.
OL,10,FHer election follows the retirement of
OL,11,Fthe Bishop of Bangor, Andrew John, who
OL,12,Fheld the office of Archbishop of Wales
OL,13,Ffor three-and-a-half years.
OL,15,FHe stepped down in August after two
OL,16,Freports published concerns about
OL,17,FBangor Cathedral. One detailed reports
OL,18,Fof inappropriate behaviour, lack of
OL,19,Fboundaries and excessive alcohol
OL,20,Fconsumption.
