OL,6,FAt the time, the Church in Wales said
OL,7,Fit takes safeguarding extremely
OL,8,Fseriously. The former Archbishop said
OL,9,Fthe findings "offer (...) opportunity
OL,10,Ffor change". There was no suggestion
OL,11,Fthat Andrew John behaved
OL,12,Finappropriately.
OL,14,FThe Church in Wales has since called
OL,15,Ffor a number of reviews and
OL,16,Finvestigations of Bangor diocese and
OL,17,Fcathedral following "deeply troubling"
OL,18,Frevelations.
