OL,3,CChurch in Wales announces first female
OL,4,CArchbishop
OL,6,FCherry Vann was chosen from among the
OL,7,Ffive serving Welsh bishops to become
OL,8,FWales' 15th Archbishop and the first
OL,9,Fwoman to hold the position.
OL,11,FReacting to the news, she said: "The
OL,12,Ffirst thing I shall need to do is to
OL,13,Fensure that the issues which have been
OL,14,Fraised in the last six months are
OL,15,Fproperly addressed and that I work to
OL,16,Fbring healing and reconciliation, and
OL,17,Fto build a really good level of trust
OL,18,Facross the Church and the communities
OL,19,Fthe Church serves."
