OL,3,CChurch in Wales announces first female
OL,4,CArchbishop
OL,6,FShe was elected having secured a two-
OL,7,Fthirds majority vote from members of
OL,8,Fthe Electoral College on the second
OL,9,Fday of its meeting at the St Pierre
OL,10,FChurch and Hotel in Chepstow. She will
OL,11,Fbe enthroned at Newport Cathedral at a
OL,12,Flater date.
OL,14,FOriginally from Leicestershire, Cherry
OL,15,Fwas consecrated as Bishop of Monmouth
OL,16,Ffive years ago.
