OL,6,FBefore that, she was among the first
OL,7,Fwomen to be ordained as a priest in
OL,8,Fthe Church of England in 1994. She
OL,9,Fthen served as Archdeacon of Rochdale,
OL,10,Fin the Diocese of Manchester, for 11
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FShe lives with her civil partner Wendy
OL,14,Fand their two dogs and was also a
OL,15,Fmember of The Church in England's
OL,16,FArchbishops' Pastoral Advisory Group,
OL,17,Fcharged with creating resources to
OL,18,Fhelp churches welcome LGBTQI+ people.
