OL,3,CChurch in Wales announces first female
OL,4,CArchbishop
OL,6,FThe Very Revd Ian Black, Dean of
OL,7,FNewport, welcomed the news on behalf
OL,8,Fof the Diocese of Monmouth.
OL,10,FHe said: "Cherry is the right person
OL,11,Ffor this moment in the Church in
OL,12,FWales' life. She has the skills and
OL,13,Fvision that we need to restore trust
OL,14,Ffollowing some very public failings.
