OL,6,F"She has brought stability to the
OL,7,FDiocese of Monmouth, managing the
OL,8,Fchange to ministry areas with clarity
OL,9,Fand purpose, showing deep care for the
OL,10,Fclergy and people. This foundation
OL,11,Fwill be a good base as she leads the
OL,12,FProvince over the next few years.
OL,14,F"She has a deep faith, which is also
OL,15,Fopen to those who take a different
OL,16,Fview to her, and this has impressed
OL,17,Fthose people enormously.
